                  <a href="http://localhost:3000/user/stuart-w-cordell" title="Stuart W. Cordell"><img alt="Stuart W. Cordell" class="callout" height="40" src="http://s3.amazonaws.com/com.theciviccommons.production/avatars/669/standard/GRC12205-Cordell, Stuart W5x7.jpg?1299853289" title="Stuart W. Cordell" width="40"></a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cols call-out">
              <a href="/conversations/the-urban-suburban-divide-and-what-we-can-do-about-it--2">
